history.text: Hi
Hello! I've just seen Iron Man for the first time. Do you like super hero movies?
Sometimes!
I liked the Spiderman reboot
Who stars in Iron Man?
Robert Downey Jr. is Tony Stark, the alter-ego of the super hero Iron Man. I really think Robert Downey Jr. is perfect for the role; he's a great 'everyman' just like Tony Stark.
Who else stars?
The movie is based on a comic?

Gweyneth Paltrow is the sexy assistant/love interest. Terrence Howard is an Air Force weapons developer. And Jeff Bridges makes an appearance as Tony Stark's Judas after he betrays him and tries to force him out of his own company.
Haha
Great cast!
Rotten Tomatoes score?
The movie was based on Stan Lee's comics from the 60s! They really did a good job updating it.
94%! Can you believe it? It really was the start of the big super hero trend.
Wow amazing
what was your favorite scene?
The beginning of the movie when Tony Stark realizes his first idea of the 'Iron Man' was absolutely wicked. Watching him shred terrorists apart while shirking off bullets and even an RPG was intense.
Why does he transform into Iron Man?

Tony Stark is ambushed and kidnapped by terrorists in the desert of Afghanistan. While captured one of the prisoners with him implants an electromagnet in him to save him from shrapnel. Tony Stark pretends he will build these terrorists a missile but, unbeknownst to them, he actually creates a super solder suit.
That's insane!
I didn't realize he was implanted with an electromagnet
Who directed the film?
Jon Favreau directed this film. He has directed a lot of Marvel's super hero movies.
Oh man, that guy does it all
He's also an actor,, I remember seeing him on Friends back in the day
Any genre too! Elf was one of my favories of all time.
I had no idea he directed Elf
Wow
When did Iron Man come out?
Iron Man released in 2008. It really doesn't feel like a decade. The movie really holds up.
Any sequels?
There have been 2 official sequels, Iron Man 2 and Iron Man 3. Tony Stark has also appeared in other Marvel movies.
What other movies?
Avengers! Robert Downey Jr. is great for comic relief in those. I'm excited for Infinity War.
That's cool
Is this a Marvel film?
Yes, this is supposed to be the epitome of the comic book genre come to the screen. It will tie up story lines from many separate franchises within their cinematic universe.
Anything else to share about the film?
They almost had Tom Cruise play Iron Man! I think that would've been awful.
Test
